            <lg xml:id="TK371">
<l>ākūḻāṟ ṟōṉṟu macaiviṉmai kaipporuḷ </l>
<l>pōkūḻāṟ ṟōṉṟu maṭi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Perseverance comes from a prosperous fate, and idleness from an adverse fate.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
